name: MSR Isopro Fuel 450g Canister
description: For use with MSR® canister stoves, the fuel is clean-burning, 80/20 blend of Isobutane and propane.Fuel maintains pressure from 55psi per gram down to 30psi per gram, so it functions well even as the canister empties.Self-sealing Lindal valve.Contains 450g of fuel.
